---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import LandingFooter from '../components/LandingFooter.astro';
---

<LandingLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CheckMyRental"
  description="Privacy Policy for CheckMyRental property inspection services"
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="legal-page" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 2025</p>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>CheckMyRental, operated by Altam CO LLC, collects the following types of information:</p>

        <h3>1.1 Personal Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Property owner name and phone number</li>
          <li>Tenant name and phone number (provided by the property owner for scheduling)</li>
          <li>Property addresses and access information</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed securely through third-party payment processors)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.2 Property Documentation Data</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Photos and documentation from property visits</li>
          <li>Documentation reports and findings</li>
          <li>Maintenance history and HVAC service records</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>1.3 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Browser type and device information</li>
          <li>Basic website analytics (page views)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Providing property documentation services</li>
          <li>Scheduling and coordinating documentation visits</li>
          <li>Delivering documentation reports and photo documentation</li>
          <li>Processing payments and maintaining billing records</li>
          <li>Communicating about services, appointments, and updates</li>
          <li>Improving our services and website functionality</li>
          <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Third-party vendors who assist with payment processing, cloud storage, and business operations</li>
          <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or government request</li>
          <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
          <li><strong>With Your Consent:</strong> When you authorize us to share information with third parties</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>SSL/TLS encryption for data transmission</li>
          <li>Secure cloud storage with encryption at rest</li>
          <li>Access controls and authentication requirements</li>
          <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
        </ul>
        <p>However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
        <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data (subject to legal retention requirements)</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-Out:</strong> Unsubscribe from marketing communications</li>
          <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> Request your data in a portable format</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@checkmyrental.io">info@checkmyrental.io</a></p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies and tracking:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Basic website analytics to understand page views</li>
          <li>Essential cookies for website functionality</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not use cookies for advertising or tracking across other websites.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your information for as long as necessary to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide our services</li>
          <li>Comply with legal, tax, and accounting obligations</li>
          <li>Resolve disputes and enforce our agreements</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Documentation photos and reports are typically retained for 7 years for record-keeping purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under 18 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>9. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date. Significant changes will be communicated via email or prominent notice on our website.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <p><strong>Altam CO LLC (CheckMyRental)</strong></p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@checkmyrental.io">info@checkmyrental.io</a></p>
          <p>Phone: <a href="tel:8132520524">(813) 252-0524</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <LandingFooter />
</LandingLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding-top: 100px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.98) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.98) 100%);
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-page {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fc 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem;
  }

  .legal-container h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-container h1 {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .last-updated {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-section h2 {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .legal-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-section h3 {
    color: #333;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-section p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    list-style: disc;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .legal-section li {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: #e74c3c;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  body.light-mode .contact-info {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-container {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .legal-container h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .legal-section ul {
      margin-left: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
